Package it.unipr.sowide.actodes.configuration

Class PropertiesGroup

java.lang.Object
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.configuration.PropertiesGroup
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Configuration
public class PropertiesGroup
extends Object
implements Serializable
The PropertiesGroup class maintains a set of properties that are usually used for configuring a particular object of an application.
